{"tid":2010062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（印中大戰）邊境爆衝突　150士兵毆鬥釀11傷","createTime":"2020-05-10T07:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:57:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"99ef95067f96dc720c4ac85b2ff9f78986aaa3ff","tid":2010062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200510/photo/bkn-20200510131222496-0510_00952_001_01p.jpg?20200510152116\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200510131222496-0510_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20200510152116&h=eb986b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國和印度的邊界糾紛持續，兩國軍人上周六（9日）在錫金邦北部的中印邊境爆發肢體衝突，雙方互相毆打，造成4名印度士兵及7名中國士兵受傷。<br />\n<br />\n《印度時報》引述印方2名軍官消息指，事發於錫金邦北部的「Naku La」地區，印度士兵當日巡邏期間遇上中方士兵，突然爆發激烈衝突，互相拳打腳踢；約150名中印軍人參與其中，最終導致11人受傷，而衝突在地方層面上已經解決。有前軍官透露，Naku La傳統上不會引起衝突。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年8月，兩國軍隊曾於拉達克地區班公湖附近爆發衝突，當時雙方擲石攻擊對方，雙方均有人受傷，最終兩軍在半小時後退回各自據點。同年，中印軍隊曾在洞朗地區對峙73日，其後雙方決定撤退，令兩國關係緩和。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200510/mobile/bkn-20200510131222496-0510_00952_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0463425c7b5a4860d103b4aa312b57e4ef3df8ed","tid":2010062,"uid":54373,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"石頭又輸<br />\n拳頭又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae26dfebd24f74ae6af071ba56053be0b72940be","tid":2010062,"uid":66378,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"大家都有槍有炮，但就係鐘意掉石頭用拳頭"},{"pid":"dd9f84ba070288142863a17c2b12dfde0a632198","tid":2010062,"uid":125026,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ae26dfebd24f74ae6af071ba56053be0b72940be","tid":2010062,"uid":66378,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,